Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.96,1:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a blessing.\N>> Uh very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.92,1:11:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the spiritual pathway is\Ngratifying and pleasurable
