Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.44,1:11:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Dr. Hawkins, can you clarify for me\Nuh if there is no crossover between the
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.36,1:11:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,animal realm and the human realm in\Nreincarnation terms? For example, uh dog
