Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.28,1:12:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,>> No. Who said it did?\N>> I I understood that creation and
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.56,1:12:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution are one in the same thing. And\NI I I can get my head around that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.48,1:12:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,>> What did you think?\N>> Creation and evolution are one of the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.23,1:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,can't get understand that concept.\N>> Oh yeah. Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.84,1:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation is what evolution looks like.\NWhat creation looks like
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.64,1:12:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you can create a thing already. You can\Ncreate a cake already cooked
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.00,1:12:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or you can put the batter in and you put\Nit in the oven and you turn it up and
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.56,1:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you see it rise and become its\Nfulfillment of its potential.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.15,1:12:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So we inherited was a potential and\Nevolution is the uh is the emergence of
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.71,1:12:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of what it looks like.\N>> Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.80,1:12:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So the universe was created\Nin an evolutionary design. You might say
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.84,1:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it was created to be evolutionary.\NYes. God's will was that there would to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.84,1:13:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,be was to be no end. That evolution is\Nan ongoing continuous progression.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.88,1:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And then when we look back then we then\Nwe say okay this is because of that and
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.80,1:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,etc etc.\N>> It's not because of
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.88,1:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,>> oh no it's not because of no you think\Nof causality. No, emergence means uh
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.19,1:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,this potentiality actualizes when local\Nconditions are appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.12,1:13:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a potential and it actualizes\Nif lo if conditions are favorable. It's
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.32,1:13:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,not forced to if it doesn't rain, it's\Nnot going to not going to the ceiling
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.60,1:13:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,will not grow without rain. So,\Nbut it's set up from evolution that the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.88,1:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,seed plus warmth plus the sun plus\Nmoisture
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.76,1:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,has the potentiality to emerge as the\Nsee
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.36,1:14:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> but it's not forced to do so. Mhm. And\Nobviously it's up to local conditions
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.76,1:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because if it doesn't rain the seed will\Nnot evolve, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.80,1:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah. Yeah. I can see that. I think the\Nrest of it will get clear in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.08,1:14:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> No, don't you think don't think of it in\Nterms of causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.48,1:14:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This phase does not cause the next phase\Nwhich does not cause the next. So you're
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.23,1:14:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,superimposing a Newtonian\Ndialogue upon it of causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.19,1:14:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything. Everything\Nis merely becoming
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.96,1:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the ful fulfillment of his own\Npotentiality,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.88,1:14:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not being caused to do so.\N>> So, so a a dog's soul, as it were,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.40,1:14:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, would that\Nfor its the potentiality of of where
