Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.84,1:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,believed she would commit suicide.\N>> Oh. Uhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.92,1:20:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay. I learned about it by chance.\N>> Uhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.76,1:20:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And they wanted to tell her the truth\Nfor some time, but then I decided not
