Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.23,1:20:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are absolute.\NUh there's no no right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.76,1:20:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, every decision you make\Ndoesn't involve right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.12,1:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, whether I should put this\Nshirt on or another shirt is not a
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.88,1:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,matter of right and wrong. It's only a\Nmatter of choice. So, you're free to
