Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.56,1:26:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that you do.\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.80,1:26:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> My question is at what point does making\Nmoney become a quest for gain?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.28,1:26:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At what point\N>> when does when does it cross over from
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.23,1:26:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,just making money to pay your bills and\Nbecome a quest for for gain because you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.63,1:26:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,recommend that we give up gain?\N>> Oh
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.12,1:26:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,well a gain is the way you're holding\Nit.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.67,1:26:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Nwhat is money? Then you have to define
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.28,1:26:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what is money and what does it\Nrepresent.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.63,1:27:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And is it a a pleasure or is it a\Nnecessity? Is it a goal in itself?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.76,1:27:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a badge of merit? You know, some\Npeople it's a badge of merit, a bigger
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.15,1:27:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,house, a bigger car, etc., etc. So,\Nmoney is a fun thing spiritually because
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.92,1:27:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it has so many different meanings. You\Nsee, with your worth more, if you were
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.12,1:27:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,worth more, God would provide with with\Nmore, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.60,1:27:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Nso at each point along the way your
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.76,1:27:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship with money takes on a\Ndifferent significance
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.15,1:27:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore it's an interesting point\Nof reference periodically throughout
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.00,1:27:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,your life. See and uh then in the end\Nwhen you lose all interest in it becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.88,1:27:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,important because you can't survive\Nwithout it. So you say well you can't
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.48,1:27:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,just kiss it all goodbye and well you\Ngoing to live in a poor folks home. They
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.08,1:27:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,won't let you in there.\N>> Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.23,1:27:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So it has different meaning and\Nsignificance and value.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.80,1:28:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And Rama Krishna wouldn't let let\Nany of his students touch money. He
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.08,1:28:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,thought money was contaminated.\NAnd I've always disagreed with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.56,1:28:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said it's not the money. It's the\Nenergy with which you hold it. It's your
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.08,1:28:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship to the money, not the money\Nitself. The money itself is just a piece
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.00,1:28:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of paper.\NIt's just a piece of paper. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.80,1:28:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And that so it changes.\N>> It changes. It changes constantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.12,1:28:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay.\N>> You can see it is a gift from God. You
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.48,1:28:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,say, "Thank you, Lord, for this gift\Nwithout which I would not be able to
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.28,1:28:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,continue physically or I'd have to keep\Nmy old job, which was a killer." You
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.00,1:28:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,know what I mean?\N>> I like that. That's great. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.19,1:28:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,very much.\N>> So is is valuable. It's valuable. What
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.96,1:28:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,does money mean to me now? What did it\Nmean to me in the past?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.12,1:28:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What value could it have for me in the\Nfuture?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.96,1:29:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's important in today's society.\NYou can't ignore it. You can't ignore
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.76,1:29:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,money. I think that's a false attitude.\NYou can't live in this world without
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.52,1:29:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,money.\N>> Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.15,1:29:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There used to be a consciousness\Nexpansion program years ago and somebody
