Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.52,1:29:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ears, you can't live in this world\Nwithout money.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.48,1:29:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,really creates creates kind of a\Nconundrum if you're if you have a
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.04,1:29:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,business and you need to pay your bills\Nbut yet you you don't want it to become
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.08,1:29:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,always a question of well how much am I\Ngoing to make when I do this? How much?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.76,1:29:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So it's a matter of balance. Yes.\N>> Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.76,1:29:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,>> It's worth effort but not your life.\N>> Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.63,1:29:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Not worth your dedicating your life to\Nbut
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.84,1:30:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> thank you so much.\NHuh?
