Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.40,1:30:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> will there be a transfer of energy?\N>> Oh, will there be a transfer of energy
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.92,1:30:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if you hold her necklace? I don't know\Nthat
