Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.08,1:31:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of my doing so calibrates\Nover 500,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.48,1:31:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,600,\N700.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.67,1:31:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of my doing so. Therefore,\Nto do so is permissible as an act of
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.19,1:31:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,love. Resist. Okay. As an act of love.\NYes. Thank you.
