Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.88,1:38:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,much higher calibration. He may act in a\Nway that is a higher calibration and
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.71,1:39:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes a lower one.\N>> No, because you're confusing appearance
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.00,1:39:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and essence. uh the essence doesn't\Nchange just because the appearance does.
